<HEADLINE> Zambian President Calls For Collective </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, January 16 (Xinhua) -- Zambian president Frederick
Chiluba called here today on his countrymen to assume collective
responsibility, collaborate and work hard to eradicate poverty
and attain political, social and economic prosperity of their
