UKWAAG, which is less than a year old, has a number of British
oil and gas supply and service companies as members, and more
companies are being encouraged to join and take advantage of the
combined resources, market information and export initiatives
from the group.
</P>
<P>
The aims and objectives of the group also include coordinating
action between British companies in pursuit of large oil and gas
projects.
</P>
