<HEADLINE> Lebanese, Syrian Presidents to Meet on Peace </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIRUT, January 16 (Xinhua) -- Lebanese President Elias Hrawi
is scheduled to visit Syria Saturday to discuss with his Syrian
counterpart Hafez al Assad the Middle East peace process and
Lebanese internal affairs.
