<TEXT>
<P>
A total of 16,635 completely built-up vehicles were imported
last year, down 49.9 percent from 33,224 in 1996, while duties in
baht terms totaled 9,413 million baht, down 51 percent, local
press reports Saturday quoted the department as saying.
