"Xinhua Daily Telegraph"
</P>
<P>
-- Chinese President Jiang Zemin Friday met with a delegation
from the Federal Express, a U.S. air freight company, led by its
board chairman Federick Smith. Jiang also met with Henry Schacht,
chairman of Lucent Technologies in the United States.
</P>
<P>
